item.title: CVE-2023-4811|2024-08-02T07:38:00.704Z -- unknown -- wordpress%20file%20upload
item.description: The WordPress File Upload WordPress plugin before 4.23.3 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as contributors to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
